<div class="rebranding_container">
  <div class="text-image-block_wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-center-sb">
    <div class="text-image-block_wrapp-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <h2 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">
          Gucci logo: 
        </span>
        a key to authenticity
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text">
        The Gucci logo is a crucial element in determining the authenticity of a Gucci bag. When examining the logo, it should be precise, clear, and symmetrical. Look for any signs of poor quality, such as blurry or uneven lines, misspelled words, or incorrect font styles. 
<br><br>
A genuine Gucci logo features a distinctive font style, with the letters “G” and “U” being slightly larger than the other letters. Additionally, the logo should be centered and evenly spaced. Any deviation from these characteristics can be a red flag indicating a fake Gucci bag.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class="text-image-block_wrapp-image text-image-block_wrapp-image-small" src="{{ "gucci-seo_logo.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Gucci logo: a key to authenticity">
  </div>
</div>

